# Benchmarks Workspace

- Benchmark tooling is a single Vite app configured in
  [bench/vite.config.ts](mdc:bench/vite.config.ts).
- Multi-page routing is handled by
  [bench/plugins/vite-plugin-multi-html.ts](mdc:bench/plugins/vite-plugin-multi-html.ts).
- Framework-specific transforms are scoped in
  [bench/plugins/vite-plugin-multi-framework.ts](mdc:bench/plugins/vite-plugin-multi-framework.ts).
- Framework implementations live under [bench/frameworks](mdc:bench/frameworks).
- Benchmark pages and manual UI tests live under [bench/src/pages](mdc:bench/src/pages).
- Shared styling lives in [bench/src/styles.css](mdc:bench/src/styles.css) and
  [bench/src/design-system.css](mdc:bench/src/design-system.css).
- Local dev notes and setup are in [bench/README.md](mdc:bench/README.md).
